00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:09.310
ALAN SEALES: Why did
you decide on 12?

00:21:09.310 --> 00:21:10.520
DAVID HEIN: We started
out at I think--

00:21:10.520 --> 00:21:11.390
IRENE SANKOFF: It
didn't start out at 12.

