trying to tell so many stories

00:21:19.750 --> 00:21:23.650
and we're Canadian, and there's
a very Canadian ethos of like,

00:21:23.650 --> 00:21:26.230
well, I got a truck and I have
a church, let's put on a show.

00:21:26.230 --> 00:21:28.563
So we figured we could probably
afford 12 people, maybe.

00:21:32.734 --> 00:21:34.150
