something really

00:21:34.150 --> 00:21:38.170
wonderful about 12 people
portraying all of these people.

00:21:38.170 --> 00:21:40.600
Every one of them plays a
local and a come from away.

00:21:40.600 --> 00:21:42.826
There's something
that's sort of--

00:21:42.826 --> 00:21:44.450
there's this great
metaphor underneath,

00:21:44.450 --> 00:21:47.629
which is we're all the
same underneath it all.

00:21:47.629 --> 00:21:49.420
And so there's something
about just casting

00:21:49.420 --> 00:21:51.670
it and having people
play multiple parts that

00:21:51.670 --> 00:21:52.480
underlines that.

